--- !u!114 &1568529986
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1568529984}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b41174f2cf012784b9994e9989c6fe23, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueObject
  currentLines:
  - Hello, again.
  - Your second mission will consist of a chain of deliveries.
  - This is the Greeper Jeeper system, so all the planets are close by. But the asteroids
    fly everywhere!
  - Keep your fuel up, and keep moving!
  - You should rely on your hyperdrive to make these deliveries!
  - You may be also wondering what that Purple Line is!
  - Your ship has been fitted with the brand new Gas Station Locator 2000!
  - It tells you the direction to the nearest gas station.
  - Your HUD at the top left of the screen also tells you how far you are from both
    the delivery planet and a gas station.
  - Have fun, and good luck!
  currentSprites:
  - {fileID: 8347205984499736533, guid: 5bb6d6e35257b2a48bff5a4299441b71, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8347205984499736533, guid: 5bb6d6e35257b2a48bff5a4299441b71, type: 3}
